collection.name: Global Self Storage - Sadsburyville
collection.description:
At Global Self Storage our motto is "Security is Our First Priority". Global Self Storage – Sadsburyville offers you a clean, safe and secure storage solution. We are conveniently located off W. Lincoln Highway and Aim Boulevard, and with easy access to Business Route 30 to ensure quick access to your self storage unit.

Global Self Storage – Sadsburyville features the very best in today’s technology in order to keep your items safe and secure. We offer state of the art security, with keypad coded electronic gates and 42 cameras that record 24/7. Along with the video recording, we conduct regular lock checks. If that isn’t safe enough, we’ve designed the self storage buildings to act as a perimeter along with fencing to play a role in keeping your belongings safe. To help make your storage experience a great one we’ve built out every unit with roll up doors. We always keep our facility well lit and clean to avoid any hazards that might sneak out and trip you up. For our interior units we offer a convenient service elevator so you don’t have to move all those boxes up the stairs. We know that putting your items into storage is normally accompanied by some large life change or shift taking place, our hope is to make the storage process as easy as possible. Call our location today to speak to one of our trained professionals.
Storage Units Sadsburyville Features:

 FIRST FULL MONTH'S RENT FOR FREE if planning to rent at least 90 days and elect for auto pay with a credit card available on Climate Controlled units only at this time.
FREE Move In truck. See manager for details
24 Hour access
 24/7 Video Security Recording
 24/7 Rental & Payment Center
 24/7 Keypad Coded Access
 Climate controlled units available
 Tenant’s Storage Insurance available – starting at $2000 coverage for $9 a month
 Fully fenced facility with security lighting
 Month-to-month rental agreements available
 Many sizes available, from 5x5ft to 10x30ft
 Online payment options
 Moving & Packing Supplies available for all your packing needs
 RV, Car, Boat Parking available
 Professional Global Self Storage Specialists with your security in mind
